### 2. Scroll-Driven Animations

**Library:** [GSAP](https://greensock.com/gsap/) + [ScrollTrigger](https://greensock.com/scroll/)

```javascript
// Basic scroll trigger
gsap.to('.element', {
  scrollTrigger: {
    trigger: '.element',
    start: 'top 80%',      // when top of element hits 80% of viewport
    end: 'bottom 20%',
    scrub: 1,              // smooth scrubbing (1 second delay)
    markers: false,        // set true for debugging
    toggleActions: 'play none none reverse'
  },
  y: 100,
  opacity: 0.5,
  scale: 1.2
});

// Parallax effect
gsap.to('.parallax-bg', {
  scrollTrigger: {
    trigger: '.section',
    start: 'top bottom',
    end: 'bottom top',
    scrub: true
  },
  y: '-20%'
});

// Pin section during scroll
ScrollTrigger.create({
  trigger: '.pinned-section',
  start: 'top top',
  end: '+=500',           // pin for 500px of scroll
  pin: true,
  pinSpacing: true
});
```

**Easing Functions:**
- `power1.out` - Smooth deceleration
- `power4.out` - Strong deceleration (dramatic)
- `expo.out` - Exponential ease (snappy)
- `elastic.out(1, 0.3)` - Bouncy effect
- `CustomEase` - Create custom bezier curves

