### 3. Text Animations

**Library:** GSAP SplitText (Club GreenSock)

```javascript
// Character-by-character reveal
const split = new SplitText('.headline', { 
  type: 'chars,words,lines',
  charsClass: 'char',
  linesClass: 'line'
});

gsap.from(split.chars, {
  scrollTrigger: { trigger: '.headline', start: 'top 80%' },
  y: 100,
  opacity: 0,
  rotationX: -90,
  duration: 1,
  stagger: 0.02,          // 20ms delay between each char
  ease: 'power4.out'
});

// Word-by-word reveal
gsap.from(split.words, {
  y: 50,
  opacity: 0,
  duration: 0.8,
  stagger: 0.1,
  ease: 'power3.out'
});

// Line reveal with mask
gsap.from(split.lines, {
  yPercent: 100,
  duration: 1,
  stagger: 0.1,
  ease: 'power4.out'
});
```

**CSS for masking:**
```css
.line {
  overflow: hidden;
  display: block;
}
```

