### Key Takeaways from Sanrita.ca

| Technique | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| **Same-world staged reveal** | Makes loading feel like world expansion, not a separate preload screen |
| **Map as interface** | Reinforces "exploration" theme |
| **Scroll story points** | Progressive content revelation |
| **Topographic overlays** | Adds depth, continuity, and cartographic texture |
| **Animated route lines** | Makes progress feel spatial rather than numeric |
| **Lime green accents** | High contrast on earthy backgrounds |
| **Split-screen layout** | Persistent navigation + context |
| **Vertical edge labels** | Editorial/magazine aesthetic |

